Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.69,0:00:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, eat!\NThe weisswurst here is especially good!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.00,0:00:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it delicious?\NUmm...Dieter, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.07,0:00:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, if you don't eat anything,\NDieter will eat it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.24,0:00:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no need to worry, Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.74,0:00:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,This place is safe.\NOnly regulars come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.08,0:00:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,If a stranger comes around\NOtto here will drive them out.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.35,0:00:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Business has been bad\Nsince I've been doing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.69,0:00:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Who ordered the spätzle?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.43,0:00:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that would be me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.70,0:00:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I made a bed in the attic.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.93,0:00:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You can sleep peacefully if\Nyou can ignore the rats.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.60,0:00:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Otto.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.47,0:00:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,He's unsociable,\Nbut he's a good guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.07,0:01:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, you can't do battle\Non an empty stomach!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.14,0:01:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for everything,\Nand for finding me a room.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.61,0:01:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I should be the one thanking you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.98,0:01:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd be in the morgue right now\Nif you hadn't saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.86,0:01:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I can eat good food like this\Nbecause I'm alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.16,0:01:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.80,0:01:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I've contacted Dr. Gillen.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.47,0:01:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,He's also relieved that we found you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.30,0:01:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,He left an ad calling out to you\Nin the newspaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.61,0:01:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's talk about our memories\Nof cheating"...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.21,0:01:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You knew?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.84,0:01:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.11,0:01:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you contact him–?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.62,0:01:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't want to get him involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.69,0:01:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be so reserved.\NFriends are good to have.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.59,0:01:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what's this about you\Nkeeping watch over me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.53,0:01:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The Richard Braun case...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.00,0:01:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Richard?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.54,0:02:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The time he shot a young serial killer\Nwhile working on the police force.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.68,0:02:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,While I was reading the article,\NDieter saw the boy's picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.48,0:02:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,He said that boy was\Nin 511 Kinderheim.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.62,0:02:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,511 Kinderheim?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.96,0:02:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It was an East German orphanage.\NA very special one.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.16,0:02:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Dieter's foster parent was\Nan instructor there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.83,0:02:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,He kept a lot of pictures of\Nthe children that were there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.90,0:02:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to the orphanage?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.57,0:02:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Johan was also there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.21,0:02:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you saying that\Nthere's a connection
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.34,0:02:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,between Johan and the boy\Nthat Richard shot?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.21,0:02:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.88,0:02:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Richard was dead before I\Ncould get the details from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.39,0:02:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw you in front of Richard's grave...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.89,0:02:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Richard...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.89,0:03:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's as if he led you to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.93,0:03:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You've done your best\Nby yourself until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.10,0:03:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're not alone anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.14,0:03:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Your innocence will be proven.\NJohan is right before your eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.08,0:03:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The photograph...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.45,0:03:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no. I left it in the office!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.02,0:03:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,We would have understood everything\Nif I showed you Johan's photo...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.02,0:03:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That man who was trying to\Nkill you probably...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.73,0:03:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,He probably destroyed it, didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.96,0:03:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That man...came into counseling with\Nhis wife under the name Hesse.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.20,0:03:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I tried to contact him,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.87,0:03:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,but there was nobody by\Nthe name of Hesse.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.14,0:03:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Johan is right before our eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.58,0:03:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,He's here.\NThat means we can meet him, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.28,0:03:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.78,0:03:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I can meet Johan...in person.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.84,0:05:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Thalbach & Schuwald AG...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.98,0:05:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The company at the center of\Nthe Schuwald financial group.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.58,0:05:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Schuwald hardly ever went out in public,\Nbut lately has.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.96,0:05:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Around this time in the morning,\Nhe goes to his affiliated companies.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.86,0:05:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's something that Richard discovered\Nwhen he was still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.86,0:05:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Not only this company,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.80,0:05:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,but all the businesses in\Nhis financial group
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.30,0:05:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,have seen a huge growth in profits ever\Nsince that boy became his right-hand man.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.81,0:06:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Here he comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.82,0:06:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Schuwald's the one in the wheelchair.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.22,0:06:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Karl's the one pushing him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.26,0:06:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.62,0:06:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So is that him?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.79,0:06:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,There's...no mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.99,0:06:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.99,0:06:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.86,0:06:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the first time I've seen\NJohan in broad daylight.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.37,0:07:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. Let's bring everything out\Ninto the light!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.84,0:07:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my only chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.41,0:07:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Now's your only chance\Nto prove your innocence!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.11,0:07:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,But for now, you should keep\Nhiding out in Otto's attic.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.38,0:07:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll prove your innocence soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.02,0:07:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Richard's file is around here...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.96,0:07:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.76,0:07:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad I took it home with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.47,0:07:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.74,0:07:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a little longer, Richard.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.98,0:07:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll avenge you soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.11,0:07:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,We've cornered Johan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.51,0:07:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,We've found Dr. Tenma,\Nthe decisive witness.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.99,0:07:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,All that's left...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.99,0:07:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All that's left is to find someone\Nwho saw Richard the night he died.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.99,0:07:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,There's got to be someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.46,0:07:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Once we do,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.49,0:08:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll be able to prove that Johan was\Nthe man who was with you that night.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.13,0:08:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if we can't do that,\Nthere's Fahren,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.23,0:08:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,the student who claimed he was\NSchuwald's son and committed suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.64,0:08:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,If we can find the prostitute he visited,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.84,0:08:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,then we'll be able to prove that the boy\Nwho accompanied him was Johan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.81,0:08:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's not all!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.68,0:08:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be able to\Nfind out who Johan is
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.49,0:08:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,if we question the couple who say\Nthey're Johan's parents!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.42,0:08:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That's because we've found\NJohan Liebert's grave.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.66,0:08:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,We've closed a trap around Johan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.10,0:08:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, Dr. Tenma...\NI think of Richard when I look at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.28,0:08:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's as if you're trying to shoulder\Nthe burdens of the entire world.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.88,0:08:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're not alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.28,0:08:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,There's Dieter and\NDr. Gillen and myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.62,0:09:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Things are all right now.\NRest easy tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.27,0:09:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I didn't want to\Nget him involved!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.34,0:09:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is the first time.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.74,0:09:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is the first time I've seen\NJohan in broad daylight.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.08,0:09:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is my only chance...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.09,0:09:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Y-You're...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.69,0:09:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Quickly run away!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.72,0:09:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Quickly!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.67,0:09:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Reichwein speaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.64,0:09:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is Gillen.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.71,0:09:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I was just about to call you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.98,0:10:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm on the way!\NWhat is Tenma doing?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.52,0:10:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,He's at the safe house.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.62,0:10:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell him firmly that he is not\Nto leave that place.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.72,0:10:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something that's bothering me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.76,0:10:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Me too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.26,0:10:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.20,0:10:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He... Dr. Tenma's not chasing\NJohan to prove his innocence.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.50,0:10:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I didn't want to believe it...\Nbut I was also worried about that!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.99,0:10:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Dieter...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.13,0:10:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.87,0:10:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenma...told me to come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.17,0:10:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Tenma?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.17,0:10:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,He left.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.51,0:10:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.78,0:11:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,He plans to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.34,0:11:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.75,0:11:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenma plans to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.89,0:11:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop him, Mr. Reichwein...\NStop him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.32,0:11:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenma's going to become\Na murderer!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.49,0:11:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's leave it at that for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.96,0:11:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say that.\NAsk me about it, Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.26,0:11:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It gets interesting from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.66,0:11:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.73,0:11:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll ask you about it next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.83,0:12:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The third woman I killed...\NThis one is great.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.81,0:12:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.67,0:12:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.61,0:12:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you think she screamed\Nwhen I strangled her?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.48,0:12:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.58,0:12:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen to me, Doctor.\NThat woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.99,0:12:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did you go, Tenma–?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.60,0:12:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,We finally meet, Dr. Gillen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.70,0:12:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.40,0:12:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Lunge of the BKA.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.91,0:12:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard rumors about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.98,0:12:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You've apprehended several of the serial\Nhomicide offenders I'm researching.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.92,0:12:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I've read your book.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.19,0:12:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.93,0:13:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Transcendental Criminal Psychology.{\i0}\NA wonderful book!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.43,0:13:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no other essay that goes so far\Ninto the mind of a serial killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.74,0:13:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Especially the study on Heinz Kaul\Nin Chapter 3 on pages 262 to 294.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.98,0:13:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I read with great interest about
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.21,0:13:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,how his childhood trauma was\Nlinked to his crimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.69,0:13:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You seem well versed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.36,0:13:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I am honored that you have read\Nmy book so carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.49,0:13:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,My investigative technique also involves\Ngetting into the mind of the criminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.43,0:13:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I try to figure out their actions\Nby becoming them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.57,0:13:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems like you have quite\Nsome experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.01,0:13:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me about it later,\Nwhen we have the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.21,0:13:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems we both don't have that much\Ntime, so I'm going to ask you right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.61,0:13:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been going to Munich a lot, lately.\NHaven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.55,0:13:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.22,0:14:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, sit down.\NI won't take too much time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.13,0:14:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been seeing Professor Reichwein,\Na counseling psychologist.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.87,0:14:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You went yesterday as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.17,0:14:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. He was my professor in college.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.74,0:14:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,At the Düsseldorf University?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.07,0:14:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.67,0:14:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a brilliant neurosurgeon\Nwho was in the same class as you
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.41,0:14:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,at Düsseldorf University, wasn't there?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.58,0:14:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you trying to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.58,0:14:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you seen Dr. Tenma?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.02,0:14:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.92,0:14:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's talk about our memories\Nof cheating. Rudi."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.29,0:14:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You placed that classified ad in all the\Nleading newspapers across the country
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.67,0:14:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,from May 1 st to the 22nd.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.60,0:14:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.40,0:14:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I never thought that brilliant people\Nlike you or Dr. Tenma
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.64,0:14:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,cheated when you were students.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.18,0:14:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's good to have a best friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.98,0:15:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't really best friends with\NDr. Tenma when we were students.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.72,0:15:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Last May in Oder Park.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.82,0:15:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,With your help, the Velbert police\Nwere able to surround Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.16,0:15:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,They almost took him into custody.\NBut he escaped.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.56,0:15:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The wiretap on me malfunctioned.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.93,0:15:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You could have helped him to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.67,0:15:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,He... Dr. Tenma is innocent!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.48,0:15:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.18,0:15:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen to me with an open mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.78,0:15:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The murder of the director of\Nthe Eisler Memorial Hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.38,0:15:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,and three others in Düsseldorf.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.59,0:15:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The murder of a patient in a building\Nunder construction.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.66,0:15:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The murder in Heidelberg.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.99,0:15:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The murders of middle-aged couples\Nacross the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.56,0:15:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenma isn't the one who did them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.00,0:15:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the conclusion I have drawn\Nas a criminal psychologist
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.90,0:15:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,from interviewing him in person.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.27,0:15:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I see... So where is he right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.34,0:16:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,He's gone off somewhere again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.44,0:16:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did he run away?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.71,0:16:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would he run away\Nif he's innocent?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.92,0:16:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.62,0:16:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So why has he disappeared from you,\Nhis best friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.46,0:16:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I have proof that\Nhe isn't the culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.50,0:16:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Take a look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.70,0:16:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,This is an analysis of all the information\Nconcerning this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.03,0:16:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a considerable amount of work.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.20,0:17:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So...do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.94,0:17:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.48,0:17:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The unnatural death of Fahren,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.18,0:17:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,the boy who pretended to\Nbe Schuwald's son.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.91,0:17:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The unnatural death of Richard Braun,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.21,0:17:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,the ex-police detective who\Nwas investigating this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.58,0:17:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The questions surrounding\NSchuwald's illegitimate child.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.56,0:17:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a boy at the center\Nof all of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.79,0:17:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,His name is the same one\Nthat Tenma said was the real culprit
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.96,0:17:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,when he was questioned...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.50,0:17:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Johan Liebert.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.97,0:17:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The gravestone of a person with\Nthe same first and last name
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.00,0:17:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,was discovered in Bruntal.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.44,0:17:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Furthermore, someone went after\NDr. Reichwein after he picked up
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.64,0:17:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,the investigation from where\NRichard Braun left off.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.82,0:17:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.72,0:17:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.49,0:17:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It is impossible to prove that\Nall these events are connected.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.03,0:18:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenma went into hiding because\Nhe understands this the most.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.34,0:18:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.28,0:18:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Your hand movements.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.02,0:18:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Don't pay any attention to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.75,0:18:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just a mnemonic tool.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.89,0:18:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,As a psychologist, it seems to me
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.33,0:18:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,that your anxiety is manifesting\Nitself in your hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.23,0:18:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the same. instead of my hand,\NI have my cassette recorder.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.43,0:18:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But the sound that's recorded\Non this tape is objective.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.24,0:18:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The information that you remember\Nthrough your hand movements
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.98,0:18:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,immediately becomes tainted\Nwith your opinions.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.88,0:18:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That's probably how you've done\Nyour job until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.22,0:18:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You believe that\Nyour hand's memory is correct–
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.25,0:19:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,that your judgment isn't wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.76,0:19:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have a family?\NDo you have any hobbies?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.83,0:19:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you live for your job?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.40,0:19:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you ever made a mistake?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.87,0:19:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you terribly afraid\Nto make a mistake?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.47,0:19:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,To you, Tenma has to be a bad person.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.41,0:19:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,If not, then your self-identity would suffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.71,0:19:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at the truth.\NThis is a photograph of Johan Liebert.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.46,0:19:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you prove that\Nthese are all Tenma's lies?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.80,0:19:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This boy... Where is he right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.11,0:19:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a student of the University of\NMunich.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.41,0:19:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,At the moment, he's Schuwald's\Nsecretary.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.95,0:20:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you mind if I hold on\Nto this photograph?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.69,0:20:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,From here on,\Nthis is a matter for the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.69,0:20:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I might have made a terrible mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.13,0:20:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is Dr. Tenma right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.70,0:20:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,H-He should be in Munich.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.46,0:20:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...this is Lunge.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.32,0:20:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Get me the Munich police.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.96,0:20:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to request\Nemergency deployment.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.63,0:20:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenma is within the city of Munich.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.54,0:21:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,A sniper rifle?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.84,0:21:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.61,0:21:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You should have had a call\Nfrom Mr. Heitmeyer
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.72,0:21:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,from the mountain villa in Fussen.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.79,0:21:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,10,000 marks in advance.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.12,0:21:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I have it ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.36,0:21:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Your order is a little troublesome,\Nso it'll take a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.47,0:21:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Meanwhile, do something about\Nthat pale body of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.91,0:21:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a waste if you have a lot of\Ngood tools, but can't use them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.98,0:21:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Next in the news.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.78,0:21:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A reception was held for the\NMunich Electronics Industry Trade Fair{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.29,0:21:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}which is going to be hosted next week\Nby the state chamber of commerce.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.93,0:21:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Leading political and business figures\Nfrom all over the world have gathered.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.26,0:21:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}With the formation of the EU,\Nthe industries of Bavaria{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.87,0:21:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}are trying to become\Nthe center of the new media network.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.87,0:22:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This will be the largest trade fair\Nthat this city has ever hosted.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.24,0:22:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hans Georg Schuwald' who hasn't\Nappeared in public for nearly 20 years{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.98,0:22:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}attended this reception and received an\Napplause from the whole audience.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.18,0:22:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mr. Schuwald was in a wheelchair,\Nbut he appeared healthy{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.32,0:22:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and demonstrated his vitality to political\Nand business figures in attendance.{\i0}
